<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
		<title>Ver O Peso Virtual • Nova conta</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/base.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/login.css">
	</head>
	<body>
		<section class="prompt">
			<h3>Registre-se Para </h3>
			<p>Monetizar suas receitas. 
				Ganhar dinheiro ao cozinhar seu prato favorito e muito +</p>

			<form action="/signup" method="post">

				<section>
					<label for="username">Registre um Username</label>
					<input id="username" name="username" type="text" autocomplete="username" required>
				</section>

				<section>
					<label for="new-password">Registre um Senha</label>
					<input id="new-password" name="password" type="password" autocomplete="new-password" required>
				</section>
				
				<button type="submit">Registrar</button>
			</form>

			<p class="help">Já tem conta? <a href="/login">Entrar</a></p>
		</section>

		<footer class="info">
			<p>Created by <a href="">Equipe 5</a></p>
			<p>Part of <a href="https://todomvc.com">DevS Pai D'agua</a></p>
			<p>Authentication powered by <a href="">UFPA</a></p>
		</footer>

	</body>
</html>
